{"lemma":"سَبُوحَةٍ","slug":"سَبُوحَةٍ","root":"س.ب.ح","root_slug":"س-ب-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ب-ح","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18669","n18672"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18669","headword_ar":"سَبُوحٌ","root":"sbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAbiHN","text_ar":"سَابِحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n18672","headword_ar":"سُبُّوحٌ","root":"sbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~uwHN","text_ar":"سَبُّوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, Msb, K, &c.,) the latter the more agreeable with analogy, but the former the more common, (Th, T, S, Msb, *) one of the epithets applied to God, (T, S, A, Msb, * K,) because He is an object of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasobiyH","text_ar":"تَسْبِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and [often] immediately followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qud~uwsN","text_ar":"قُدُّوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) which is likewise also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qad~uwsN","text_ar":"قَدُّوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", though the former pronunciation is the more common: (Th, T, S, Msb: *) it signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"All-perfect, all-pure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all-glorious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far removed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free, from everything evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, Mgh, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and from every imperfection"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb. [See 2, and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suboHaAna A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"سُبْحَانَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) It is said (S, Msb) by Th (S) that there is no word like the two epithets above, of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fE~uwl","text_ar":"فعُّول"},{"kind":"text","text":"with damm as well as with fet-h to the first letter, except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~wH","text_ar":"ذرّوح"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) but the following similar instances have been pointed out:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"st~wq","text_ar":"ستّوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"among epithets, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~wH","text_ar":"ذرّوح"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$b~wT","text_ar":"شبّوط"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~wj","text_ar":"فرّوج"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sf~wd","text_ar":"سفّود"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kl~wb","text_ar":"كلّوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"among substs. (TA.) Sb says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa fiY AlkalaAmi fuE~awolN","text_ar":"لَيْسَ فِى الكَلَامِ فُعَّوْلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biwaAHidapK","text_ar":"بِوَاحِدَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~aAHN","text_ar":"ذُرَّاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) [or] accord. to AHei, Sb said that there is no epithet of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlN","text_ar":"فُعُّولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sub~uwHN","text_ar":"سُبُّوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qud~uwsN","text_ar":"قُدُّوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": Lh mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sut~uwqN","text_ar":"سُتُّوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, as an epithet applied to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diroham","text_ar":"دِرْهَم"},{"kind":"text","text":", as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sat~uwqN","text_ar":"سَتُّوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","A","Msb","Zj","Mgh","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}